    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generic term for materials derived from vinyl chloride, vinyl acetate, or vinylidene chloride. Commonly used with reference to all polymers and copolymers of which vinyl chloride is a constituent. Use more precise terminology for known materials such as "polyvinyl chloride" or "polyvinyl acetate."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
